    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="General-MAC-frame-format"><a href="#General-MAC-frame-format" class="headerlink" title="General MAC frame format"></a>General MAC frame format</h2><center><img src="/../images/802154_mac_frm/1_general_format.png" alt="frm_type" width="600px"></center><br/><h3 id="frm-control"><a href="#frm-control" class="headerlink" title="frm control"></a>frm control</h3><center><img src="/../images/802154_mac_frm/3_frm_control.png" alt="frm_type" width="500px"></center><br/><h5 id="mac-frm-type"><a href="#mac-frm-type" class="headerlink" title="mac frm type"></a>mac frm type</h5><center><img src="/../images/802154_mac_frm/2_frm_type.png" alt="frm_type" width="350px"></center><h5 id="Security-Enabled"><a href="#Security-Enabled" class="headerlink" title="Security Enabled"></a>Security Enabled</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Security Enabled = 1（启用安全性）：</span><br><span class="line">    该帧受到 MAC 子层安全机制 保护；</span><br><span class="line">    MHR（MAC 帧头）中必须包含 辅助安全头部 (Auxiliary Security Header) 字段。</span><br><span class="line">Security Enabled = 0（未启用安全性）：</span><br><span class="line">    该帧不受 MAC 子层保护；MHR 不包含 辅助安全头部。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br/><h5 id="Security-Enabled-1"><a href="#Security-Enabled-1" class="headerlink" title="Security Enabled"></a>Security Enabled</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Frame Pending（帧挂起）字段用于指示发送设备是否还有 更多数据 需要发送给接收设备。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">字段规则</span><br><span class="line">•Frame Pending = 1（有数据待发送）：</span><br><span class="line">    发送设备仍有待传输的数据帧。</span><br><span class="line">    接收设备可继续监听信道以接收后续数据。</span><br><span class="line">•Frame Pending = 0（无数据待发送）：</span><br><span class="line">    发送设备没有待传输的数据帧。</span><br><span class="line">    接收设备可以关闭无线电以节省能耗。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">适用场景</span><br><span class="line">1.信标帧 (Beacon Frame)：</span><br><span class="line">    Frame Pending 字段可用于指示 PAN 设备是否有待发送的数据给某个子设备。</span><br><span class="line">2.启用信标的 PAN (Beacon-Enabled PAN)：</span><br><span class="line">        设备在CAP（竞争访问周期）期间发送数据时，可以使用该字段指示是否仍有待发送的数据。</span><br><span class="line">3.非信标 PAN (Non-Beacon-Enabled PAN)：</span><br><span class="line">    设备可以在任何时间使用该字段，提示接收方是否需要保持接收状态。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">特殊模式中的行为</span><br><span class="line">•低功耗 CSL 模式（LE CSL Mode）：</span><br><span class="line">    Frame Pending = 1 时，表示发送设备仍有待传输数据，希望接收设备保持无线电开启直到 Frame Pending 变为 0。</span><br><span class="line">•TSCH 模式（时隙通信，Time-Slotted Channel Hopping）：</span><br><span class="line">            Frame Pending = 1 时，表示接收设备应该在下一个时隙继续监听，即使没有预定的通信链接。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">忽略情况</span><br><span class="line">•除了上述情况外，在其他时间发送的帧中，Frame Pending 字段应设为 0，并且接收方应忽略该字段。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br/>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
